    <item>
      <title>New Look for 2012 and a Special Announcement</title>
      <link>/2011/12/29/new-look-for-2012-and-a-special-announcement/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Dec 2011 07:30:01 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>/2011/12/29/new-look-for-2012-and-a-special-announcement/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Happy New Year, everyone!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In the spirit of renewal, new ideas, and new beginnings, we&#39;ve upgraded the look of the site for 2012.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I&#39;m sure you&#39;re thinking about new things to bring into your life in the coming year too...and as it just so happens, I have a couple of ideas for you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Tune in next week for a special announcement that you won&#39;t want to miss if you&#39;re a regular reader here.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The thing is, we&#39;re only going to tell our newsletter subscribers about it for now.&lt;/strong&gt; If you&#39;re not already on the list (getting regular blog updates by email), then you probably want to sign up at the bottom of this post.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Of course, we&#39;ll eventually share the news with everyone through a public blog post too, but not for a few more weeks.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;So sign up before Friday to get the special announcement!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I hope 2012 brings you lots of new energy,&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dan&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
